propDescriptions.size: The size of the component. It accepts theme values between 'sm' and 'lg'.
propDescriptions.sx: The system prop that allows defining system overrides as well as additional CSS styles. See the `sx` page for more details.

slotDescriptions.li: The component used to render the li.
slotDescriptions.ol: The component used to render the ol.
slotDescriptions.root: The component used to render the root.
slotDescriptions.separator: The component used to render the separator.
